      <title>中国与菲律宾在谈判中对新海域热点提出主权要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-philippines-hold-talks-as-new-hotspot-emerges-in-sea-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和菲律宾在周三的外交官会议上坚持对南海新热点地区提出各自主权要求，尽管双方都在寻求缓解紧张局势的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-philippines-hold-talks-as-new-hotspot-emerges-in-sea-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 16:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
